# Cloud Build context — what gets uploaded to gcloud builds submit.
# Production credentials are injected via Dockerfile --build-arg
# (VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID, VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY, VITE_API_URL, VITE_WS_URL)
# pulled from Secret Manager at submit time. We intentionally exclude
# all .env files so a stale local copy can never override the build
# args or leak into the bundle.

.git
.gitignore
.gcloudignore
node_modules/
dist/
.DS_Store
*.log

# Local dev / agent state — never ship to the build context
.claude/
.env
.env.*
NETRUN_CAD_WEB_WHITEPAPER_v1.0.md
DESIGN.md
